cydramanager-db/cydraos:
The files in this folder contains one line having their versions.
If you find a file having text in more than the first line this is a bug.

cydramanager-db/cydraos/instructions:
There should be the same number of files in this folder as in cydramanager-db/cydraos.
Inside them you will find the build instructions for the package in five categories:
 - dependency: a list of all dependencies of the package
 - build:      configure and build the package
 - install:    install the package
 - download:   contains only one line which is the link to download the package
dependency should always be present even if the package dont have any.
If you see a file not respecting the usual typography please report it.
